snippet.title: Persona 4: Dancing All Night Gameplay (E3 2015)
snippet.description:
http://www.GameXplain.com
Yukiko shows off her hot moves while dancing to a remix of Snowflakes in this gameplay demo of Persona 4: Dancing All Night at E3 2015!
